{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras/logo_a_rescaled.png?t=1720884962\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras/TWITTER.png?t=1720884962\" /><br>The <strong>definitive</strong> western poncho roguelite experience.<br>Embark on a trip through hell as Poncho Rodriguez, the most ruthless outlaw from the Wild West.<br>Go on a rampage while enjoying the dynamic electro-western music.<br>Meet creatures that will try to help or (and) kill you and reclaim what you were stolen...<br>Build your best card deck which you can bet on the saloon in a surreal <strong>dice poker game.</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras/cartas_en_rs.gif?t=1720884962\" /><br>Upgrades come in the shape of cards. Choose thoughtfully and prepare yourself for the next levels.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Weapon cards: Reveal unique weapons with different play styles.<br></li><li>Upgrade cards: Upgrade your stats and modify your weapons to the limit.<br></li><li>Dice: Gather different special dice to increase your chances in the poker game.<br></li><li>Collectibles: Find these rare collectibles to learn about Poncho's story...</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras/apuesta_en_rs.gif?t=1720884962\" /><br>Try your luck on a dice game against the fellows you find in the saloon, make your build even stronger, or start from zero.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3017150/extras/armas_en_rs.gif?t=1720884962\" /><br>Apply modifications to your weapons, go for a hell-destructive build covering the whole level in bullets, or you may prefer to go slowly with your sniper shooting from afar...<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"http